content: Bishui Cave is a Secret Area found in Chapter 5 of Black Myth: Wukong. Below you'll find a guide to accessing the cave by defeating the Five Element Carts and information on the bosses you'll find inside, including the ferocious Bishui Golden-Eyed Beast.

Bishui Cave is a Secret Area found in Chapter 5 of Black Myth: Wukong. Below you'll find a guide to accessing the cave by defeating the Five Element Carts and information on the bosses you'll find inside, including the ferocious Bishui Golden-Eyed Beast.
